# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your key.
# If ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is set, the AI Match page uses it server-side and
# visitors don't need to bring their own key. If it's unset (as on a
# personal deployment you want to keep free), visitors are prompted to paste
# their own key, which is stored only in their browser's localStorage.

# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
